</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">My rough, inaccurate-but-useful model =
of Robinhood Markets Inc. is:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; pad=
ding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">It i=
s a big retail brokerage that has done a lot to change investing over the p=
ast few years and is one of the most important companies in the financial i=
ndustry, but</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Nobody who works ther=
e has ever met a securities lawyer.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">N=
ot fair, I know! (Its <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/25254005.273335/aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLnJvYmluaG9vZC5jb20vbmV3cy8yMDIwLzUvNS9=
kYW4tZ2FsbGFnaGVyLXJvYmluaG9vZC1ib2FyZC1tZW1iZXItYW5kLWZvcm1lci1zZWMtY29tbW=
lzc2lvbmVyLWpvaW5zLXJvYmluaG9vZC1hcy1jaGllZi1sZWdhbC1vZmZpY2Vy/607f07ceef4b=
8524a319a23cB40253c4a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targe=
t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">general counsel</a> actually used to be an S=
EC commissioner?) And yet. The scandals that it keeps having are=C2=A0<em>w=
eird</em>, like, just one level more=C2=A0<em>amateurish </em>than the scan=
dals that=C2=A0other important=C2=A0financial firms have. It once announced=
 that it would give its customers bank accounts, but then various regulator=
s called it up and said =E2=80=9Cuh you=E2=80=99re not a bank?=E2=80=9D and=
 by the=C2=A0<em>next day=C2=A0</em>it had <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/25254005.273335/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS=
9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMTItMTcvcm9iaW5ob29kLWNoZWNraW5nLW1vdmVkLWZhc=
3QtYW5kLWJyb2tl/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBbaa24780" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" i=
temscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> pulled the prod=
uct</a>. Its great business innovation was to=C2=A0creatively use=C2=A0paym=
ent-for-order-flow revenue to subsidize commission-free trading in a way th=
at was both commercially successful for Robinhood and also probably good fo=
r most of its customers, but instead of advertising that smart move it <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25254005.273335/aHR0cH=
