y1tYXJrZXQtd2FzLXRvby1nb29k/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB366813af" itemprop=3D"=
StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #00000=
0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> spe=
nt years lying about it</a> and got in trouble with the Securities and Exch=
ange Commission.=C2=A0This summer the Financial Industry Regulatory Authori=
ty=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25254005.2=
73335/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZmlucmEub3JnL21lZGlhLWNlbnRlci9uZXdzcmVsZWFzZXMvMjAyM=
