itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">fined Robinhood=
 $57 million</a>, =E2=80=9Cthe largest financial penalty ever ordered by FI=
NRA,=E2=80=9D largely for <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/25254005.273335/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGl=
