aking the law=E2=80=9D is, in ordinary circumstances, bizarrely pointless a=
nd confrontational, but if there=E2=80=99s going to be a confrontation anyw=
ay Robinhood might as well strike first.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In=
